cc:Work.dc:title: No new oil, says polar bear protestor
cc:Work.dc:description:
A polar bear in an arctic scene, with a sign that says 'NO NEW OIL'. 
 
It's a multiple remix of the following artworks: 
 
'Knut the polar bear' by aitor_avila 
http://openclipart.org/detail/3934/knut-the-polar-bear-by-aitor_avila 
 
'Ice-scape' by moini 
http://openclipart.org/detail/176625/ice-scape-by-moini-176625 
 
'Oil or gas well' by baditaflorin 
http://openclipart.org/detail/169316/oil-or-gas-well-by-baditaflorin
